SD.2 StructureDefinition-qr

source file: source/pages/_includes/qr-intro.md

The Argonaut QR profile sets the minimum expectations for the QR resource to record, search and fetch QR from simple assessments, surveys, etc as defined in this implementation guide

Scope and Usage

The Argonaut QuestionnaireResponse resource supports:

  • The completed Answer to an assessment form
  • Links to questions and assiociated scores for question-answer/answer choice
  • Because of it standardized data structure, it is shareable across systems enabling data aggregation and analysis.

(out of scope) Can be transformed to other FHIR resources (out of scope)

The Argonaut Questionnaire resource supports:

Mandatory Data Elements and Terminology

The following data-elements are mandatory:

Each Questionnaire must have:

  1. A status (Mandatory in base)
  2. A link to the question being answered (Mandatory in base)
  3. A reference to the form being answered (Mandatory in SDC)
  4. A Patient (Mandatory in SDC)
  5. A datetime (Mandatory in SDC)

The system [Must Support] if available:

  1. QuestionnaireResponse.identifier
  2. QuestionnaireResponse.author
  3. QuestionnaireResponse.source
  4. QuestionnaireResponse.item
  5. QuestionnaireResponse.item.definition
  6. QuestionnaireResponse.item.text
  7. QuestionnaireResponse.item.answer
  8. QuestionnaireResponse.item.answer.value[x]
  9. QuestionnaireResponse.item.answer.item
  10. QuestionnaireResponse.item.item

JSON Template

​
          // 
 {
   "resourceType" : "QuestionnaireResponse",
    "id" : "<id>", // Logical id of this artifact
    "meta" : {Meta}, // Metadata about the resource
    "implicitRules" : "<uri>", // A set of rules under which this content was created
    "language" : "<code>", // Language of the resource content
    "text" : {Narrative}, // Text summary of the resource, for human interpretation
    "contained" : [{Resource}], // Contained, inline Resources
    "extension": [
    ],
    "identifier" : {Identifier}, // Unique id for this set of answers
    "basedOn" : [{Reference(ReferralRequest)}], // Request fulfilled by this QuestionnaireResponse
    "parent" : [{Reference(Observation)}], // Part of this action
    "questionnaire" : {Reference([CanonicalType[http://fhir.org/guides/argonaut-questionnaire/StructureDefinition/q]])}, // R! Form being answered
    "status" : "<code>", // R! in-progress | completed | amended | entered-in-error | stopped
    "subject" : {Reference([CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition/us-core-patient]])}, // R! The subject of the questions
    "context" : {Reference(Encounter)}, // Encounter or Episode during which questionnaire was completed
    "authored" : "<dateTime>", // R! Date the answers were gathered
    "author" : {Reference([CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition/us-core-practitioner], CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition/us-core-patient], CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Device], CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/RelatedPerson]])}, // Person who received and recorded the answers
    "source" : {Reference([CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition/us-core-practitioner], CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/StructureDefinition/us-core-patient], CanonicalType[http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/RelatedPerson]])}, // The person who answered the questions
    "item" : [{ // C? Groups and questions
      "extension": [
      ],
      "linkId" : "<string>", // R! Pointer to specific item from Questionnaire
      "definition" : "<uri>", // ElementDefinition - details for the item
      "text" : "<string>", // Name for group or question text
      "subject" : {Reference(Resource)}, // The subject this group's answers are about
      "answer" : [{ // C? The response(s) to the question
        "extension": [
        ],
// value[x]: Single-valued answer to the question. One of these 9:
        "valueDecimal" : <decimal>, // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueInteger" : <integer>, // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueDate" : "<date>" // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueDateTime" : "<dateTime>", // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueTime" : "<time>", // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueString" : "<string>", // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueUri" : "<uri>", // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueCoding" : {Coding}, // Single-valued answer to the question
        "valueQuantity" : {Quantity}, // Single-valued answer to the question
// value[x]: Nested groups and questions. One of these 0:
      }],
// value[x]: Nested questionnaire response items. One of these 0:
    }],
  }
